details.description: Dining table with 2 extensions. Room for 2-4 diners; the length of the table can be adjusted as needed. 6 drawers under the table surface for storing napkins, cutlery, candles, etc. This table is tested to the highest standards of strength , Stability and safety to withstand daily use in your home for years.
details.good_to_know: The small dimensions of a table make it easy to integrate with the furniture, even when space is limited.
